Once Upon a Time in China II;;1992;;R;;Action,Adventure,Biography;;7.4;;Hark Tsui;;Jet Li,Rosamund Kwan,Siu Chung Mok,David Chiang,Donnie Yen,Tielin Zhang,Xin Xin Xiong,Paul Fonoroff,Shi-Kwan Yen,Ka-Kui Ho,Michael Miller,Dion Lam,Shu-Kei Chow,Joseph Chi,Chuen Chiang,Siu-Wah Chan,Chi-Hung Ling,Kwai Po Chun;;In the sequel to the Tsui Hark classic, Wong Fei-Hung faces The White Lotus society, a fanatical cult seeking to drive the Europeans out of China through violence, even attacking Chinese who follow Western ways. Wong must also defend Dr. Sun Yat Sen, a revolutionary, from the military. With his friends, loved ones, and the future of China itself at stake, Wong must once again use his martial arts skills to defend the innocent.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0105839/